data.description: Welcome to this very well maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of the highly rated Ocean Springs School District on 1/4 acre lot.  As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting open floor plan accentuated by cathedral ceilings in the living room as well as a cozy *fireplace* that adds warmth and charm to the space. The kitchen boasts a large bar area, ample counter and cabinet space adorned with elegant granite countertops, and all major appliances including a refrigerator.  Adjacent to the kitchen and dining area lies an **additional spacious family/flex room** which has great views of the backyard and a custom sitting area tucked between custom shelving on both sides.  The primary bedroom includes a walk in closet and ensuite bathroom that features double vanities, a luxurious soaker tub, and a separate stand-up shower, providing the ultimate in relaxation and convenience.  Outside, the spacious backyard is fully fenced and shaded by mature trees, creating a private oasis perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day.  Make your appointment today!
